Q. For each hospital service, calculate the total number of patients admitted, total patients refused, and the admission rate (percentage of requests that were admitted). Order by admission rate descending.

SELECT service, 
SUM(patients_admitted) AS total_admitted, 
SUM(patients_refused) AS total_refused, 
CAST(SUM(patients_admitted) * 100.0 / SUM(patients_request) AS DECIMAL(5,2)) AS admission_rate_percent
FROM services_weekly
GROUP BY service
ORDER BY admission_rate_percent DESC;
